<td>10</td>
<td>50</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>If the average installation time is 30.2 minutes, find missing frequencies.</p</p></div><div><strong>Answer:</strong><br><style>body .mathjax_wrap{width: 100%;overflow-x: scroll;margin-bottom:10px;}</style><p>Let x and y be the missing frequencies. Now, Let&#8217;s construct the table:</p>
<p>Given, x̄ = 30.2</p>
<div class="table_wrapper" style="overflow-x:auto;"><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="width: 25%;">class(x)</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">No.(f)</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">m</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">fm</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 25%;">0-10</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">4</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">5</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">20</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 25%;">10-20</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">x</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">15</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">15x</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 25%;">20-30</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">10</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">25</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">250</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 25%;">30-40</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">y</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">35</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">35y</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 25%;">40-50</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">10</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">45</td>
<td style="width: 25%;">450</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="width: 25%;"></td>
<td style="width: 25%;">N = 50 = 24 + x + y</td>
<td style="width: 25%;"></td>
<td style="width: 25%;">Σfm = 720 + 5x + 35y</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>Now, from table</p>
<p>24 + x + y = 50</p>
<p>x + y = 26  &#8212;&#8212;&#8212; (i)</p>
<p>Also,</p>
<p>15x  + 35y + 720 = 30.2 x 50</p>
<p>15x + 35y = 790 &#8212;&#8212;&#8212;&#8211;(ii)</p>
<p>Solving equation i) and ii)</p>
<p>\(\frac{\begin{matrix} 15x \enspace + \enspace 15y \enspace = \enspace 390\\ 15x \enspace + \enspace 35y \enspace<br />
= \enspace 790 \end{matrix}}{ &#8211; 20y\enspace = \enspace &#8211; 400 }\)</p>
<p>y = 20</p>
<p>When, y = 20</p>
<p>x + 20 = 26</p>
<p>x = 6</p>
<p>The missing frequencies are 20 and 6</p>
